docker.baseDockerfile:
FROM mcr.microsoft.com/azureml/openmpi3.1.2-ubuntu18.04
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends apt-utils software-properties-common build-essential libboost-all-dev zlib1g-dev cmake && pip install --upgrade pip
RUN git clone --branch 8.8.0 --recursive https://github.com/VowpalWabbit/vowpal_wabbit.git && cd vowpal_wabbit && mkdir build && cd build && cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DBUILD_TESTS=OFF -DVW_INSTALL=ON -DBUILD_PYTHON=ON -DPY_VERSION=3.6.2 && make install && cd .. && pip install .

FROM mcr.microsoft.com/azureml/openmpi3.1.2-cuda10.0-cudnn7-ubuntu16.04
USER root
RUN mkdir -p /etc/OpenCL/vendors && echo "libnvidia-opencl.so.1" > /etc/OpenCL/vendors/nvidia.icd
RUN apt-get update && echo 'success updated apt-get!'
RUN apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends cmake libboost-dev libboost-system-dev libboost-filesystem-dev
RUN conda create -n gpuexp python=3.6.2 -y

###############################
# Pre-Build LightGBM
###############################
RUN cd /usr/local/src && mkdir lightgbm && cd lightgbm && \
    git clone --recursive --branch v2.3.0 --depth 1 https://github.com/microsoft/LightGBM && \
	cd LightGBM && mkdir build && cd build && \
	cmake -DUSE_GPU=1 -DOpenCL_LIBRARY=/usr/local/cuda/lib64/libOpenCL.so -DOpenCL_INCLUDE_DIR=/usr/local/cuda/include/ .. && \
	make -j4

###############################
# Install GPU LightGBM and XgBoost
###############################
RUN /bin/bash -c "source activate gpuexp && \
    cd /usr/local/src/lightgbm/LightGBM/python-package && python setup.py install --precompile && \
	pip install --upgrade --force-reinstall xgboost && \ 
	source deactivate"

FROM mcr.microsoft.com/azureml/intelmpi2018.3-ubuntu16.04
RUN pip install azureml-defaults==0.1.0.* --extra-index-url https://azuremlsdktestpypi.azureedge.net/dev/aml/office/134157926D8F --no-cache-dir && pip install azureml-telemetry==0.1.0.* --extra-index-url https://azuremlsdktestpypi.azureedge.net/dev/aml/office/134157926D8F --no-cache-dir && pip install azureml-dataprep==2.0.2 --no-cache-dir && python -c "from dotnetcore2 import runtime; runtime.ensure_dependencies()"
RUN pip install --index-url https://azuremlsdktestpypi.azureedge.net/SideCar-Release/D89B478218CC/ --no-cache-dir azureml-sidecar==1.6.0
ENV AZUREML_SIDECAR_PREP_CMD="[\"azureml.sidecar.sidecar\", \"--task\", \"prep\"]"
ENV AZUREML_SIDECAR_RELEASE_CMD="[\"azureml.sidecar.sidecar\", \"--task\", \"release\"]"
ENTRYPOINT ["python", "-m", "azureml.sidecar.sidecar", "--task", "start_cms"]
